<h2>Managing SQL</h2>

<p>SQLite is <a href="http://sqlite.org/serverless.html">serverless</a>. The whole DB is one single file. It requires no username or password, and you cannot connect via TCP/IP - you <em>must</em> use the filesystem to access the file.</p>

